{
  "version": 5,
  "description": "E库 CIDR 段漏斗式画像标签 v5。标签按顺序执行，每个标签在前面标签的剩余池上工作。",
  "tags": [
    {
      "id": "cloud_service",
      "name": "☁️ 云服务商",
      "emoji": "☁️",
      "color": "#ff6a00",
      "logic": "AND",
      "description": "云服务商 IP 段(58段/1,805 IP)。高设备密度，WiFi主导(98.5%)。典型云/代理出口特征。",
      "conditions": [
        {"field": "top_operator", "op": "IN", "value": ["阿里云","腾讯云","华为云","百度云","亚马逊","微软","京东云","天翼云","UCloud","金山云"], "label": "运营商=云服务商"}
      ],
      "notes": "当前E库中云服务商58段/1,805 IP。"
    },
    {
      "id": "root_anomaly",
      "name": "🚨 Root异常",
      "emoji": "🚨",
      "color": "#ef4444",
      "logic": "AND",
      "description": "Root上报比例≥20%的异常段(137段/3万IP)。电信77段(avg_root_ratio=34.5%)、联通52段(31.0%)、移动8段(30.9%)。Root占比高是典型的设备篡改/群控特征，不适合作为正常网络标签。",
      "conditions": [
        {"field": "root_report_ratio", "op": ">=", "value": 0.20, "label": "Root占比 ≥ 20%"}
      ],
      "notes": "137段中，电信77段avg_ip=107，联通52段avg_ip=418，移动8段avg_ip=10。排在前面确保后续标签不会命中这些段。"
    },
    {
      "id": "mobile_telecom",
      "name": "📶 移动出口·电信",
      "emoji": "📶",
      "color": "#58a6ff",
      "logic": "AND",
      "description": "中国电信移动NAT出口(5,595段/191万IP)。移动占比≥85%，DAA/DNA avg=13.2，dev/IP=84.7。",
      "conditions": [
        {"field": "top_operator", "op": "=", "value": "中国电信", "label": "运营商=中国电信"},
        {"field": "mobile_device_ratio", "op": ">=", "value": 0.85, "label": "移动占比 ≥ 85%"},
        {"field": "daa_dna_ratio", "op": ">=", "value": 3, "label": "DAA/DNA ≥ 3"}
      ],
      "notes": "与H库 mobile_telecom 对齐。"
    },
    {
      "id": "mobile_unicom",
      "name": "📶 移动出口·联通",
      "emoji": "📶",
      "color": "#f97316",
      "logic": "AND",
      "description": "中国联通移动NAT出口(297段/15.5万IP)。dev/IP=355。",
      "conditions": [
        {"field": "top_operator", "op": "=", "value": "中国联通", "label": "运营商=中国联通"},
        {"field": "mobile_device_ratio", "op": ">=", "value": 0.85, "label": "移动占比 ≥ 85%"},
        {"field": "daa_dna_ratio", "op": ">=", "value": 3, "label": "DAA/DNA ≥ 3"}
      ],
      "notes": "联通段数少但单段IP多(avg=522 IP/段)。"
    },
    {
